tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE qualitative_research_data (
    observation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_id INT,
    observation_text TEXT,
    observation_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE DataAnalysis (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    researcher_id INT,
    observation_id INT,
    theme_id INT,
    code_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE
);
